                  </div>             
            </div>              
            
          </div>

          <div class="text-center border-top" style="margin-top: 50px;">
              <h4 style="margin-top: 50px;">We have different style</h4>

              <p style="font-size: 1.2em; padding: 40px;">Pass <code>&set=set7</code> to generate different set of avatar. </p>             

              <code>https://avatar-api.org/avatar.svg?name=Dian Sastro Wardoyo&set=set7</code> <i class="fa fa-long-arrow-right"></i> will generate <img src="https://avatar-api.org/avatar.svg?name=Dian Sastro Wardoyo&set=set7">

            <div class="text-center" style="padding: 30px; font-size: 1.3em; font-weight: 500;">Other example</div>

            <div class="row" style="margin: 0px 50px;">
