                  </div>             
            </div>              
            
          </div>          

          <div class="text-center border-top" style="margin-top: 50px;">
              <h4 style="margin-top: 50px;">Custom color as you wish</h4>

              <p style="font-size: 1.2em; padding: 40px;">Pass <code>&color=tomato</code> to specify any color. It accept CSS color code such as <code>midnightblue</code> or hex code such as <code>#f576ac</code> or to get a surprise you can also put <code>random</code>.</p>             

              <code>https://avatar-api.org/avatar.svg?name=Sundari Sukotjo&set=set7</code> <i class="fa fa-long-arrow-right"></i> will generate <img src="https://avatar-api.org/avatar.svg?name=Samantha Albert&color=tomato">

